      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下FinTech系统的自动化文档流程。核心是从TransactionQueue开始，交易数据推送到LedgerService进行入账处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
