    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是push模式，LedgerService作为收件箱被动接收。然后LedgerService会用classify-inbox.mjs脚本把分类后的数据送回TransactionQueue，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
