        "Classified"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了TransactionQueue推送到LedgerService，再用脚本返回的循环。接下来呢？",
